# Slice Conventions

- Import design tokens: `import { theme } from "@/lib/master-theme"`
- Import company data: `import { company } from "@/lib/company"` (never hardcode)
- Use Prismic components: `PrismicRichText`, `PrismicNextImage`, `PrismicNextLink`, `PrismicText`
- Type props: `SliceComponentProps<Content.XxxSlice>` from `@prismicio/client` and `@prismicio/react`
- Wrap in `<section data-slice-type={slice.slice_type} data-slice-variation={slice.variation}>`
- Server component by default (no `"use client"` unless interactive elements)
- Use Prismic MCP tools for content modeling: `how_to_model_slice`, `how_to_code_slice`, `save_slice_data`
- model.json and mocks.json are managed by Slice Machine — edit via MCP tools or Slice Machine UI, not manually
